






@(1 = 1-8) Say to my lord, and repeat to my kid of the mountains, with beautiful horns; to my horse of the mountains, with an eagle's claws; my date-palm, growing on untouched ground and with fresh (?) dates hanging from it: this is what the captain of pledged 
{troops
} 
{@noteanchor{2 mss. have instead:} soldiers
} , @wPN{Aba-indasa} -- who, by means of prayers for his king, greatly pleases his king's heart -- your servant, says:


@(9 = 9-10) You are mighty, 
