@(14 = 14-15) I am a scribe and I write on stelae.
{@noteanchor{2 ms. add:} …… business concerning the troops.
}  I will …… business which has been neglected in the assembly, when it …….
{@noteanchor{1 ms. adds:} …… business which makes good …… equal.
